project-root/
├── storyline/          # Your Storyline HTML5 files go here
│   ├── story.html
│   ├── story_content/
│   └── mobile/
├── api/                       # Serverless API endpoints
│   ├── generate-script.js     # Calls OpenAI to generate a script
│   ├── create-video.js        # Sends script to HeyGen to generate a video
│   └── get-video.js           # (Optional) Checks video generation status
├── .env                       # Your API keys (not committed to Git)
├── .gitignore                 # Includes .env
├── vercel.json                # Optional config (routes, build settings)
├── package.json               # Project metadata (used if you need npm packages)
└── README.md                  # (Optional) Project notes